title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 14900
description:
It would be nice if some kind person added a Karaoke section under Audio so we did not have to post under Other.   300 CDG+MP3 Karaoke songs optomised for great search results on a PC or Mac.  The 2015 collection now includes multiple Karaoke Label choice on the more popular songs for the very first time.

To increase swarm size this collection is posted both on the Pirate Bay and KAT.

Torrent is seeded for 24 hours or until the number of seeds are greater than the number of Peers, which ever comes first.   Then it is up to the community to decide if that torrent sinks or swims as I need all my upload bandwidth to seed the next part in this series and unlike films each torrent contains 600 files and there is no way on this earth I can possible seed all the torrents in this series since number 250.  That would be almost 30,000 open files.  Good luck with that.

I use super seeding for the first hour or so depending on the number of Peers in the first swarm.

Rigmar Radio - Seeding to the World since 2004
